iles/2021/04/Block-Patterns.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://ja.wordpress.org/files/2021/04/Block-Patterns-1024x575.png?resize=632%2C414&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³\" class=\"wp-image-6157\" srcset=\"https://ja.wordpress.org/files/2021/04/Block-Patterns-1024x575.png 1024w, https://ja.wordpress.org/files/2021/04/Block-Patterns-300x169.png 300w, https://ja.wordpress.org/files/2021/04/Block-Patterns-768x431.png 768w, https://ja.wordpress.org/files/2021/04/Block-Patterns.png 1264w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒã‚„ãƒ—ãƒ©ã‚°ã‚¤ãƒ³ãªã©ã€WordPress ã®ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã‚¨ãƒ‡ã‚£ã‚¿ãƒ¼ã§ä½•ã‹ã‚’ä½œã£ãŸã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‚‹äººã¯ã€<strong>ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³</strong>ã«ã¤ã„ã¦ã‚‚èã„ãŸã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‚‹ã‹ã‚‚ã—ã‚Œã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress ã«åŒæ¢±ã•ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã‚’çœºã‚ã¦ã„ã¦ã€ã“ã‚Œã«ã¤ã„ã¦çŸ­ã„è¨˜äº‹ã‚’æ›¸ãã®ã‚‚è‰¯ã„ã‹ãªã¨æ€ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¯çŸ¥ã£ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã¨ã¨ã¦ã‚‚ä¾¿åˆ©ãªã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ¼ãƒˆã‚«ãƒƒãƒˆãªã®ã§ã™ãŒã€ä¸€ä½“ä½•ãªã®ã‹ã¨ã‹ã€ä½¿ã†å ´é¢ã‚’çŸ¥ã‚‰ãªã„æ–¹ã‚‚å¤šã„ã¨æ€ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¨ã¯</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¯<strong>ã‚ã‚‰ã‹ã˜ã‚é…ç½®ã•ã‚ŒãŸãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã®é›†ã¾ã‚Š</strong>ã§ã€å¤šæ§˜ã«çµ„ã¿åˆã‚ã›ãŸã‚Šé…ç½®ã‚’å¤‰ãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã‚‹ã®ã§ã€ç¾ã—ã„ã‚³ãƒ³ãƒ†ãƒ³ãƒ„ã‚’ã‚‚ã£ã¨ç°¡å˜ã«ä½œã‚Œã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ãƒ¬ã‚¤ã‚¢ã‚¦ãƒˆã‚’ã‚¹ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒˆã™ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã®ãƒ„ãƒ¼ãƒ«ã¨ã—ã¦ã€å¿…è¦ã«å¿œã˜ã¦ã‚³ãƒ³ãƒ†ãƒ³ãƒ„ã«è¿½åŠ ã—ã¦ã™ãã«ä½¿ã†ã“ã¨ãŒã§ã€1å€‹ã®ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªã‚·ãƒ³ãƒ—ãƒ«ãªã‚‚ã®ã‹ã‚‰ã€å…¨ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸ã®ãƒ¬ã‚¤ã‚¢ã‚¦ãƒˆã®ã‚ˆã†ãªè¤‡é›‘ãªã‚‚ã®ã¾ã§ã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/03/block-library.png?resize=632%2C414&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒªå†…ã®ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³\" class=\"wp-image-10021\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¯ã€ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒªã®ã‚¿ãƒ–ã«æ ¼ç´ã•ã‚Œã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒã‚¯ã—ãŸã‚Šãƒ‰ãƒ©ãƒƒã‚°ã—ãŸã‚Šã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€ã‚µã‚¤ãƒˆã®ã‚¹ã‚¿ã‚¤ãƒ«ã§ãƒ—ãƒ¬ãƒ“ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/03/block-pattern.png?resize=632%2C413&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã®ä¾‹\" class=\"wp-image-10022\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>åŸºæœ¬çš„ã«ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¨ã¯ã€ã‚ã‚‰ã‹ã˜ã‚æŸã­ã‚‰ã‚ŒãŸå˜ãªã‚‹ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã§ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code has-small-font-size\"><code>&lt;!-- wp:group --&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"wp-block-group\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"&gt;&lt;!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} --&gt;\n&lt;hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"/&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:separator --&gt;\n&lt;!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":553,\"width\":150,\"height\":150,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} --&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"&gt;&lt;figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"&gt;&lt;img src=\"https://blockpatterndesigns.mystagingwebsite.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/StockSnap_HQR8BJFZID-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-553\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:image --&gt;\n&lt;!-- wp:quote {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} --&gt;\n&lt;blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote has-text-align-center is-style-large\"&gt;&lt;p&gt;\"Contributing makes me feel like I\'m being useful to the planet.\"&lt;/p&gt;&lt;cite&gt;â€” Anna Wong, &lt;em&gt;Volunteer&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:quote --&gt;\n&lt;!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} --&gt;\n&lt;hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"/&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:separator --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:group --&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã‚¨ãƒ‡ã‚£ã‚¿ãƒ¼ã‚’ä½¿ã£ã¦ã„ãã¤ã‹ã®ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã‚’å¥½ããªã‚ˆã†ã«è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹ã ã‘ã§ã€é›£ã—ã„ä½œæ¥­ã®éƒ¨åˆ†ã¯çµ‚äº†ã§ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒªã«å…¥ã‚Œã‚‹ã«ã¯</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ja.wordpress.org/team/handbook/block-editor/reference-guides/block-api/block-patterns/\">ãƒãƒ³ãƒ‰ãƒ–ãƒƒã‚¯ã«ã¯ã‚‚ã£ã¨è©³ã—ã„èª¬æ˜ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ãŒ</a>ã€çµè«–ã‹ã‚‰è¨€ã†ã¨ä»¥ä¸‹ã®ã¨ãŠã‚Šã§ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code has-small-font-size\"><code>&lt;?php \n/*\nPlugin Name: Quote Pattern Example Plugin\n*/\n\nregister_block_pattern(\n	\'my-plugin/my-quote-pattern\',\n	array(\n		\'title\'       =&gt; __( \'Quote with Avatar\', \'my-plugin\' ),\n		\'categories\'  =&gt; array( \'text\' ),\n		\'description\' =&gt; _x( \'A big quote with an avatar\".\', \'Block pattern description\', \'my-plugin\' ),\n		\'content\'     =&gt; \'&lt;!-- wp:group --&gt;&lt;div class=\"wp-block-group\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"&gt;&lt;!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} --&gt;&lt;hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"/&gt;&lt;!-- /wp:separator --&gt;&lt;!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":553,\"width\":150,\"height\":150,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} --&gt;&lt;div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"&gt;&lt;figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"&gt;&lt;img src=\"https://blockpatterndesigns.mystagingwebsite.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/StockSnap_HQR8BJFZID-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-553\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\"/&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /wp:image --&gt;&lt;!-- wp:quote {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} --&gt;&lt;blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote has-text-align-center is-style-large\"&gt;&lt;p&gt;\"Contributing makes me feel like I\\\'m being useful to the planet.\"&lt;/p&gt;&lt;cite&gt;â€” Anna Wong, &lt;em&gt;Volunteer&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;!-- /wp:quote --&gt;&lt;!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} --&gt;&lt;hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"/&gt;&lt;!-- /wp:separator --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /wp:group --&gt;\',\n	)\n);\n\n?&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/1f446.png\" alt=\"ğŸ‘†\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> ã“ã‚Œã¯ PHP ã®ã‚¹ãƒ‹ãƒšãƒƒãƒˆã§ã™ã®ã§ã€WordPress ã®ãƒ—ãƒ©ã‚°ã‚¤ãƒ³ã«è½ã¨ã—è¾¼ã‚“ã ã‚Šã€ã‚‚ã£ã¨ç°¡å˜ã«è¨€ãˆã°ã€ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒã®<strong>functions.php</strong> ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã«è²¼ã‚Šä»˜ã‘ãŸã‚Šã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚å®Œäº†ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/03/Quote.jpg?resize=632%2C430&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"åŒºåˆ‡ã‚Šç·šã€ä¸­å¤®é…ç½®ã®ç”»åƒã€å¼•ç”¨ã€åŒºåˆ‡ã‚Šç·šã‚’å«ã‚€ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³\" class=\"wp-image-10047\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>ç”»åƒã‚’å«ã‚€ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã§ã¯ã€ç”»åƒã‚’ã©ã“ã«ä¿å­˜ã™ã‚‹ã‹ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹æ™‚é–“ã‚’å‰²ãä¾¡å€¤ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<a href=\"https://ja.wordpress.org/themes/tt1-blocks/\">TT1 Blocks ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒ</a> (&#8220;TwentyTwentyOne Blocks&#8221; ã®ç•¥) ã§ã¯ã€ç”»åƒã‚’ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒªã«ä¿å­˜ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>æ¬¡ã®ã‚¹ãƒ†ãƒƒãƒ—</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¯ã€ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒªã‹ã‚‰æŒ¿å…¥ã—ãŸæ™‚ç‚¹ã§ãƒ¦ãƒ‹ãƒƒãƒˆã¨ã—ã¦ã®ã¾ã¨ã¾ã‚Šã‚’å¤±ã£ã¦ã—ã¾ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚ä½œã£ãŸãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã‹ã‚‰åˆ‡ã‚Šé›¢ã•ã‚ŒãŸå˜ãªã‚‹ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ã®å¯„ã›é›†ã‚ã«ãªã‚Šã€å¥½ã¿ã«åˆã‚ã›ã¦ã‚«ã‚¹ã‚¿ãƒã‚¤ã‚ºã§ãã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ã«ãªã‚‹ã®ã§ã™ã€‚ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã¯ãƒ†ãƒ³ãƒ—ãƒ¬ãƒ¼ãƒˆã§ã¯ãªãã€ã‚ãã¾ã§ã‚‚ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ¼ãƒˆã‚«ãƒƒãƒˆã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã¯ã¤ã¾ã‚Šã€ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒã®åˆ‡ã‚Šæ›¿ãˆã‚„ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ãƒ—ãƒ©ã‚°ã‚¤ãƒ³ã®ç„¡åŠ¹åŒ–ã‚’æ°—ã«ã™ã‚‹å¿…è¦ã¯ãªã„ã¨ã„ã†ã“ã¨ã§ã‚‚ã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚æŒ¿å…¥æ¸ˆã¿ã®ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯ãŒã©ã“ã‹ã«è¡Œã£ã¦ã—ã¾ã†ã“ã¨ã‚‚ã‚ã‚Šã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<p>ã¨ã¯ã„ãˆã€ã‚ã‚‹ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³ã‚’ã¨ã¦ã‚‚æ°—ã«å…¥ã£ã¦ã€ã¾ã£ãŸãã‚«ã‚¹ã‚¿ãƒã‚¤ã‚ºã›ãšã«ä½•åº¦ã‚‚ä½¿ã„ãŸã„å ´åˆã¯ã€<a href=\"https://ja.wordpress.org/2021/03/05/gutenberg-tutorial-reusable-blocks/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"6128\">å†åˆ©ç”¨ãƒ–ãƒ­ãƒƒã‚¯</a>ã«ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚‚ã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-embed-handl